  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Blessed are those, who like to suffer.\"<br>- </strong>正宗爱尔兰老西医 on Steam</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/e2e7ef5e5882013d171e18129fd5c408.poster.avif?t=1773585474\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/e2e7ef5e5882013d171e18129fd5c408.webm?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/e2e7ef5e5882013d171e18129fd5c408.mp4?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AN UNFORGIVING ADVENTURE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a <strong>cute frog</strong> lost in a not so cute vertical world of <strong>challenges</strong> and <strong>regret</strong>.<strong> Swing upwards</strong> using only your<strong> super elastic tongue</strong> and the <strong>skills you develop</strong> while playing the game – no excuses! Improve and <strong>master your abilities</strong> to finally get the frog back to where he belongs! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SWING UP, DON'T FALL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your ultimate goal is to<strong> reach the top of the game</strong>. On your way you will face challenging obstacles while your <strong>progress is constantly at stake</strong>. Only you decide your fate: <strong>Get all the way up</strong> to the top or <strong>fall back down</strong> into the depths of the well. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/c0cc71b9ddf16898c027a3d77fb782dc.poster.avif?t=1773585474\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/c0cc71b9ddf16898c027a3d77fb782dc.webm?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/c0cc71b9ddf16898c027a3d77fb782dc.mp4?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EASY TO LEARN — HARD TO MASTER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>tilt frog</strong> is played using only your<strong> mouse</strong> or <strong>controller</strong>. No strings attached. However, how you use these tools will have a dramatic impact on the outcome you experience. To rise or to fall is the difference of true mastery or foolish hybris. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPERIENCE A CRAZY STORYWORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The World of <strong>tilt frog</strong> is an odd one. Swing up alongside of <strong>mystic creatures</strong>, <strong>obsessive cults</strong> and <strong>remarkable landscapes</strong> to deliver the golden sphere to your princess.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/9399a2e1928c0c08a775f9986ca89a28.poster.avif?t=1773585474\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/9399a2e1928c0c08a775f9986ca89a28.webm?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/9399a2e1928c0c08a775f9986ca89a28.mp4?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR CHARACTER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from an arsenal of<strong> lovely animals</strong> (or even more lovely <strong>costumes</strong> that most definitely aren't frogs in disguise) to go on your journey with style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/7467951a0f2d7d766146d8c5ab15d761.avif?t=1773585474\" width=600 height=133 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SAVING BETWEEN SESSIONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the game in your pace. <strong>The game will always save your progress</strong>, so you can take a break between sessions. Beating the game in one session is just as valuable as beating it in 10 sessions — no need to start from the bottom every time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Blessed are those, who like to suffer.\"<br>- </strong>正宗爱尔兰老西医 on Steam</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/e2e7ef5e5882013d171e18129fd5c408.poster.avif?t=1773585474\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/e2e7ef5e5882013d171e18129fd5c408.webm?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/e2e7ef5e5882013d171e18129fd5c408.mp4?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AN UNFORGIVING ADVENTURE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a <strong>cute frog</strong> lost in a not so cute vertical world of <strong>challenges</strong> and <strong>regret</strong>.<strong> Swing upwards</strong> using only your<strong> super elastic tongue</strong> and the <strong>skills you develop</strong> while playing the game – no excuses! Improve and <strong>master your abilities</strong> to finally get the frog back to where he belongs! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SWING UP, DON'T FALL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your ultimate goal is to<strong> reach the top of the game</strong>. On your way you will face challenging obstacles while your <strong>progress is constantly at stake</strong>. Only you decide your fate: <strong>Get all the way up</strong> to the top or <strong>fall back down</strong> into the depths of the well. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/c0cc71b9ddf16898c027a3d77fb782dc.poster.avif?t=1773585474\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/c0cc71b9ddf16898c027a3d77fb782dc.webm?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/c0cc71b9ddf16898c027a3d77fb782dc.mp4?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EASY TO LEARN — HARD TO MASTER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>tilt frog</strong> is played using only your<strong> mouse</strong> or <strong>controller</strong>. No strings attached. However, how you use these tools will have a dramatic impact on the outcome you experience. To rise or to fall is the difference of true mastery or foolish hybris. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPERIENCE A CRAZY STORYWORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The World of <strong>tilt frog</strong> is an odd one. Swing up alongside of <strong>mystic creatures</strong>, <strong>obsessive cults</strong> and <strong>remarkable landscapes</strong> to deliver the golden sphere to your princess.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/9399a2e1928c0c08a775f9986ca89a28.poster.avif?t=1773585474\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/9399a2e1928c0c08a775f9986ca89a28.webm?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/9399a2e1928c0c08a775f9986ca89a28.mp4?t=1773585474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR CHARACTER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from an arsenal of<strong> lovely animals</strong> (or even more lovely <strong>costumes</strong> that most definitely aren't frogs in disguise) to go on your journey with style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507990/extras/7467951a0f2d7d766146d8c5ab15d761.avif?t=1773585474\" width=600 height=133 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SAVING BETWEEN SESSIONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the game in your pace. <strong>The game will always save your progress</strong>, so you can take a break between sessions. Beating the game in one session is just as valuable as beating it in 10 sessions — no need to start from the bottom every time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
